gs-behave-bdd.envVarPresets.markdownDescription:
Named presets of environment variables. Each key is a preset name, and the value is an object of environment variable key-value pairs. Use the gear icon on the test profile to switch between presets. Example:
```json
{
  "development": { "API_URL": "http://localhost:3000" },
  "staging": { "API_URL": "https://staging.example.com" }
}
```
